---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import '@/styles/globals.css';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import SeeLocations from '../components/SeeLocations.astro';
import AboutProject from '../components/AboutProject.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout title='Designo Agency Website Challenge.'>
  <!-- The Haeder -->
  <Header />
  <!-- The Main Section & Background Patterns  -->
  <main>
    <!-- Background Pattern Leaf Left -->
    <section class='relative'>
      <img
        src='/assets/shared/desktop/bg-pattern-leaf.svg'
        alt='pattern'
        class='absolute left-0 top-[267px] z-0 hidden lg:flex'
      />
    </section>
    <!--  About us -->
    <section
      class='relative md:ml-[2.44rem] md:mr-10 lg:mx-[10.31rem] lg:flex lg:flex-row-reverse'
    >
      <picture>
        <source
          media='(min-width: 1440px)'
          srcset='/assets/about/desktop/image-about-hero.jpg'
        />
        <source
          media='(min-width: 768px)'
          srcset='/assets/about/tablet/image-about-hero.jpg'
        />
        <img src='/assets/about/mobile/image-about-hero.jpg' alt='' class='' />
      </picture>
      <div
        class='relative flex flex-col items-center justify-center gap-6 overflow-hidden bg-[#E7816B] px-6 py-20 text-center md:gap-8 md:px-[3.63rem] md:py-16 lg:items-start lg:px-[5.94rem] lg:pb-[7.44rem] lg:pt-[8.44rem] lg:text-left'
      >
        <h1
          class='z-50 text-[2rem] font-medium leading-9 text-white md:text-5xl md:leading-[3rem]'
        >
          About us
        </h1>
        <p
          class='leading-1.5625rem] z-50 w-[20.4375rem] text-[0.9375rem] font-normal text-white md:w-[35.8125rem] md:text-base md:leading-relaxed lg:w-[28.625rem]'
        >
          Founded in 2010, we are a creative agency that produces lasting
          results for our clients. We&#39;ve partnered with many startups,
          corporations, and nonprofits alike to craft designs that make real
          impact. We&#39;re always looking forward to creating brands, products,
          and digital experiences that connect with our clients' audiences.
        </p>
        <!-- Mobile Pattern -->
        <img
          src='/assets/shared/desktop/bg-pattern-hero-desktop.svg'
          alt=''
          class='absolute right-[-68px] top-[-217px] z-30 md:hidden lg:hidden'
        />
        <!-- Tbalet Pattern  -->
        <img
          src='/assets/shared/desktop/bg-pattern-hero-desktop.svg'
          alt=''
          class='absolute bottom-[91px] left-[-150px] z-30 hidden md:flex lg:hidden'
        />
        <!-- Desktop Pattern -->
        <img
          src='/assets/shared/desktop/bg-pattern-hero-home.svg'
          alt=''
          class='absolute z-30 hidden lg:bottom-0 lg:left-0 lg:flex'
        />
      </div>
    </section>
    <!--  World-class talent -->
    <section
      class='relative mb-24 md:my-[7.5rem] md:ml-[2.44rem] md:mr-10 lg:mx-[10.31rem] lg:my-40 lg:flex lg:flex-row'
    >
      <picture>
        <source
          media='(min-width: 1440px)'
          srcset='/assets/about/desktop/image-world-class-talent.jpg'
        />
        <source
          media='(min-width: 768px)'
          srcset='/assets/about/tablet/image-world-class-talent.jpg'
        />
        <img
          src='/assets/about/mobile/image-world-class-talent.jpg'
          alt=''
          class=''
        />
      </picture>
      <div
        class='flex flex-col items-center justify-center gap-6 bg-[#fbf2ef] px-6 py-20 text-center md:py-[4.25rem] md:pl-[3.69rem] md:pr-[3.62rem] lg:items-start lg:px-24 lg:py-[9.63rem] lg:text-left'
      >
        <h2
          class='text-[2rem] font-medium leading-9 text-[#E7816B] md:text-[2.5rem] md:leading-[3rem]'
        >
          World-class talent
        </h2>
        <p
          class='w-[20.4375rem] text-[0.9375rem] font-normal leading-[1.5625rem] text-[#333136] md:w-[35.75rem] md:text-base md:leading-relaxed lg:w-[27.8125rem]'
        >
          We are a crew of strategists, problem-solvers, and technologists.
          Every design is thoughtfully crafted from concept to launch, ensuring
          success in its given market. We are constantly updating our skills in
          a myriad of platforms.
        </p>
        <p
          class='w-[20.4375rem] text-[0.9375rem] font-normal leading-[1.5625rem] text-[#333136] md:w-[35.75rem] md:text-base md:leading-relaxed lg:w-[27.8125rem]'
        >
          Our team is multi-disciplinary and we are not merely interested in
          form â€” content and meaning are just as important. We give great
          importance to craftsmanship, service, and prompt delivery. Clients
          have always been impressed with our high-quality outcomes that
          encapsulates their brand&#39;s story and mission.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>
    <!-- See Locations -->
    <SeeLocations />
    <!-- Background Pattern Leaf Right -->
    <section class='relative'>
      <img
        src='/assets/shared/desktop/bg-pattern-leaf-right.svg'
        alt='pattern'
        class='absolute right-0 top-[107px] z-0 hidden lg:flex'
      />
    </section>
    <!-- The real deal -->
    <section
      class='relative mb-24 md:my-[7.5rem] md:ml-[2.44rem] md:mr-10 lg:mx-[10.31rem] lg:my-40 lg:flex lg:flex-row-reverse'
    >
      <source
        media='(min-width: 1440px)'
        srcset='/assets/about/desktop/image-real-deal.jpg'
      />
      <source
        media='(min-width: 768px)'
        srcset='/assets/about/tablet/image-real-deal.jpg'
      />
      <img src='/assets/about/mobile/image-real-deal.jpg' alt='' class='' />
      <div
        class='flex flex-col items-center justify-center gap-6 bg-[#fbf2ef] px-6 py-20 text-center md:py-[5.87rem] md:pl-[3.69rem] md:pr-[3.62rem] lg:items-start lg:py-[9.63rem] lg:pl-[5.88rem] lg:pr-[5.87rem] lg:text-left'
      >
        <h2
          class='text-[2rem] font-medium leading-9 text-[#E7816B] md:text-[2.5rem] md:leading-[3rem]'
        >
          The real deal
        </h2>
        <p
          class='w-[20.4375rem] text-[0.9375rem] font-normal leading-[1.5625rem] text-[#333136] md:w-[35.75rem] md:text-base md:leading-relaxed lg:w-[27.8125rem]'
        >
          As strategic partners in our clients&#39; businesses, we are ready to
          take on any challenge as our own. Solving real problems require
          empathy and collaboration, and we strive to bring a fresh perspective
          to every opportunity. We make design and technology more accessible
          and give you tools to measure success.
        </p>
        <p
          class='w-[20.4375rem] text-[0.9375rem] font-normal leading-[1.5625rem] text-[#333136] md:w-[35.75rem] md:text-base md:leading-relaxed lg:w-[27.8125rem]'
        >
          We are visual storytellers in appealing and captivating ways. By
          combining business and marketing strategies, we inspire audiences to
          take action and drive real results.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <!-- About Your Project -->
  <AboutProject />
</Layout>
<!-- The Footer -->
<Footer />
